  Networkx-3 [IO]: G → ?
              → k_components(G, min_density)            CC=15   pure  !! ▶
              → node_connectivity(G, s, t)              CC=15   pure  !!
              → local_node_connectivity(G, source, target, cutoff) CC=7    mutation
              → _bidirectional_shortest_path(G, source, target, ignore_nodes, ignore_edges, weight) CC=3    mutation
              → _bidirectional_pred_succ(G, source, target, ignore_nodes, ignore_edges) CC=20   mutation  !!
              → nodes(G)                                CC=1    pure ■
              PURITY: 3/6 pure  BOTTLENECK: _bidirectional_pred_succ(CC=20)

  Networkx-3 [Core]: k → None
              → k_edge_subgraphs(k)                     CC=7    pure ▶
              → k_edge_subgraphs(G, k)                  CC=5    pure
              → k_edge_components(G, k)                 CC=6    pure
              → bridge_components(G)                    CC=1    pure
              → not_implemented_for(*graph_types)       CC=10   pure
              → set(name:str, value:Any) → None         CC=1    pure ■
              PURITY: 6/6 pure  BOTTLENECK: not_implemented_for(CC=10)

  Networkx-3 [NLP]: G1 → None
              → vf2pp_is_isomorphic(G1, G2, node_label, default_label) CC=2    pure ▶
              → vf2pp_isomorphism(G1, G2, node_label, default_label) CC=2    pure
              → vf2pp_all_isomorphisms(G1, G2, node_label, default_label) CC=15   mutation  !!
              → _feasibility(node1, node2, graph_params, state_params) CC=4    pure
              → _cut_PT(u, v, graph_params, state_params) CC=28   pure  !!
              → set(name:str, value:Any) → None         CC=1    pure ■
              PURITY: 5/6 pure  BOTTLENECK: _cut_PT(CC=28)


